Combine bread and pears.   Whisk eggs, milk, sugar, cinnamon, vanilla, and 3/4 of the cheese.   Pour over bread, cover and refrigerate overnight.  Pull 30-45 before baking. Bake covered @ 350 for 50-60 mins. Remove cover, sprinkle with remaining cheese, put back in oven till cheese melts.
